{"tid":1512150,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［結果不比良知重要？］沒有結果，點確保世世可保保有良知？","createTime":"2019-08-27T18:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:01:39.000Z","uid":149630,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca0ddd2c81394a7dbfdf59d79e69dc97ece7c0a","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:22:02.000Z","msg":"如果你真係選擇欺凌班警嘅細路 得罪講句你冇良知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即係面對兩難<br />\n你會選擇所謂良知<br />\n而寧接受萬世奴役之結果</span></span><br />\n明晒<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你要身段漂亮地轟烈死去ok<br />\n但我地香港人想奮勇求生</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為左所謂一時一地嘅良知<br />\n而令人間正義無法申張<br />\n作惡嘅人現無正道可以制裁到<br />\n而要求人民要同聖人咁<br />\n維持自己嘅道德<br />\n任由邪惡以無底綫之下宰殺<br />\n呢啲叫以善之名<br />\n叫人任人宰殺<br />\n名為<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">殉善</span></span></ins></strong></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">叫人為邪惡犧牲性命難<br />\n借善之名令坑殺善良人易<br />\n邪惡就係用呢個方法<br />\n慢慢令有善念有正義感嘅人口慢慢變成小數<br />\n於是世界就變成一個惡人當道之世</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲良知比結果重要嘅人<br />\n係私德良好<br />\n公德敗壞<br />\n對社會長久公義毫思考<br />\n只為自己道德感覺良好<br />\n彰顯公義或需要嘅殘酷代價<br />\n一毛亦唔想拔<br />\n想不努而獲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所謂悲智雙運<br />\n只有慈悲而無智慧<br />\n只會造成世上永恆嘅災難<br />\n只能講<br />\n你嘅良知十分廉價，毫無成本</span></span>"},{"pid":"f678e7529ea9468aa44d7a71529d1ef54141bc4a","tid":1512150,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:23:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新post！<br />\n更update！ 求幫推！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士進程請入，一個也不能少不是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99f8106a872e641162bf382a5e2839d08781afab","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204c3c4415f4c9a1be3a4d22aedc54ddcd4b7d60","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8132569667e7b2e2f61f4feea726181e5263bc3","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:39:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"916c3996f6fe723f5a43c05112db31637e0789df","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92bd76dc68e12d8a62d7da058ea7c23b6f065c33","tid":1512150,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d60cfb08039d0bb9f5dac505d5b16da13efdc0c","tid":1512150,"uid":2626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831471630d75624a6a8f6197fb6bb71ac7663a3c","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:44:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4026bed4470b019c7430aaee32853272c93d7db4","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:45:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83c97175a9b58e8c6c44a3cb5e4a28d8c561e37c","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:45:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bc13b5eb1cbac80ec31ce4f4e5b6ced979ab384","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:45:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f6c246f8236a8e62fcaa5bc04e4e33ca2d6ce55","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d60cfb08039d0bb9f