>\n<br />\n邊個同猶太人講良知</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ab9252db2efae8a50d7d260633c1e03c371f8304","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f50875d133001796cc96d7cad7ca551df482557a","tid":1512150,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"巴打good point,同我價值觀一樣,口講正義而冷眼旁觀,正係好多偽善者嘅行為"},{"pid":"3d5d172e21677563cbab41ef3891b855eb02e9c4","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99a7e457b16ace30775743f49ddb509a5fca55ac","tid":1512150,"uid":227337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77b1eee1e0b71fc368e9cdc03a885a81a2e1db38","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d52d53c17bf95afb91c6346145c228575f69968","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a49aca53ff0f43010e726a53fa2f99414b3588b7","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f585a45e8b4b3e77990350bba884a813a247410","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3da8cd8765ad1a02e124c9316971158bb9e1aa","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3c301f6fbce529f4bfe963c8f723cdff54b8d3f","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18b5dd375dd4ea5d9754ade1b870c5cf606bb369","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ea12787d679e7649ee72d1a26d85282beece7a6","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33c49606136b85d66eb459c1fb317613761adebf","tid":1512150,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"《孟子&middot;盡心下》：「「孔子曰：『過我門而不入我室，我不憾焉者，其惟鄉原乎！鄉原，德之賊也。』曰：何如斯可謂之鄉原矣？」」<br />\n譚嗣同《仁學》：「故常以為二千年來之政，秦政也，皆大盜也；二千年來之學，荀學也，皆鄉愿也。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鄉願指外貌忠厚老實，討人喜歡，實際上卻不能明辨是非的人。</span></span>"},{"pid":"10c1facd1f33e3976c56f5e4e76b4cd2f8231507","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8c9eaa3aa1a63aef23fe35caa1940cb4cd37e07","tid":1512150,"uid":72847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"c49418bb6a4e6339f8a48db697e0ba674a31a9f6","tid":1512150,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"歷史你勝利者撰寫架"},{"pid":"4ce7eea0f270fd7eab5aeeb8ba21d50c539e6a77","tid":1512150,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6c246f8236a8e62fcaa5bc04e4e33ca2d6ce55","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d60cfb08039d0bb9f5dac505d5b16da13efdc0c","tid":1512150,"uid":2626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:42:04.000Z","msg":"有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"幫推plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"樓主，你可能寫咗一篇罵稻草人嘅 Post。每人每一刻做事都有自己的底線。<br />\n<br />\n例如，有耳屎姐姐冇話佢自己在做甚麼。佢可以係入緊軍火要同來襲的人火併。她只係唔同欺負無辜的細路。你亦無問她會怎樣分辨誰是無辜細路，怎樣對付不是無辜的細路。唔通你問佢，「你做緊乜吖？」佢就要答你「咪入緊軍火整緊炸彈囉」噉？<br />\n<br />\n「結果不比良知重要」的意思就是不「不擇手段」，手段有分好壞。如果你覺得手段冇分好壞，噉你贊成特登捉一個現任警員但反警察的細路，直播凌遲嗎？贊成嗎？還是説這樣做結果不好，都係整污嘈吓佢地嘅書包結果就最好喇？<br />\n<br />\n你憑甚麽知道結果會是比較好？<br />\n<br />\n不擇手段的後果是被民主世界孤立。最終結果冇人知。突然皇天撃殺搞掂又得。噉搞掂咗係咪所有人做嘅野就係岩呢？<br />\n<br />\n請回答以下 :<br />\n1.如何分辨誰是有罪<br />\n2.有罪應如何對付<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n1.所有現警子女都有罪，不論已否離家出走。所有警員子女有責任令自己父母正法逆民的當權者。一日當權者未落台，所有執法人員和其親屬都有罪。執法人員没有拿下當權者，厄殺市民子女的未來，市民厄殺執法人員子女未來為等效還擊，是無罪。<br />\n2.用愛心做生日蛋糕畀佢地！<br />\n🍰🍰🍰"},{"pid":"30d01b5cdc0ac202c23386f023d16385c2a3549f","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a04d374cf396ab6ff118aa3f691e0079be0ab57a","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"551044ad7b69a0f817b60d88858561ed1cecac6d","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"345717e7beabe815a8dec97b69955ef22424ed23","tid":1512150,"uid":290468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:38:00.000Z","msg":"孟子入面已經講過，鄉願，德之賊也，正正就係講緊依班道德潔癖既柒頭，the goal justifies all means"},{"pid":"577278979dd5767ab1e805fcc95afe778685e16d","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35b574377b3cd6c948cdcd20bd26cb7623041d4b","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:50:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03df6bceaf5198c400b586a30c89eb3a6a2b7c3f","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96723674c2f6664d2e041d04eea822142bfa42d9","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:57:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d25aa3d5ad20d3abfbf686d2c1570aec5771d9ba","tid":1512150,"uid":313869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f79e5c75ee82d21d5ef62b4c76e01f2317c66a","tid":1512150,"uid":149630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d3990275